---
title: Honey Pork Koftas & Roast Veggie Grain Bowl with Flaked Almonds & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Freekeh is the standout grain we can’t get enough of, especially when it’s tossed with roasted veggies. Add some sweet pork
koftas on top to transform this grain veggie extravagance into something out of this world. You’ll be racing for seconds!
